title: "US29 — Request expert service (paid add-on)"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ServiceDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>RequestService
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: tap REQUEST SERVICE, confirm
  B->>C: request(serviceId, note)
  C->>G: insert service_requests (status=pending)
  note right of G: payment simulated -<br/>price fields only, no gateway
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: requested
  B-->>A: request appears under My Purchases
